title: 1968 Chevrolet Camaro Sport Coupe Two Door Hardtop

description: 1968 Chevrolet Camaro Sport Coupe two door hardtop,

250 cubic inch, 155 horspower, straight six cylinder engine; three speed manual transmission, manual steering, manual drum brakes,whitewall radial tires, rally wheels w/stainless steel trim rings and chrome-plated s.s.center caps, bucket seats, tinted windshield, radio/cassette player. Minor paint issues, some surface rust underneath.  Overall condition is clean and in good running condition. Own car since 1996, only second owner, garaged kept in Severn, MD.
